high_descs: Turn right and heads towards the sink counter.
Pick up the pink bar soap on the sink counter.
Look at the sink on your right.
Place the bar soap into the right sink, rinse the bar soap, and pick it up
Turn left and head towards the toilet and turn to face it.
Place the bar soap in the bin to the right of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed bar soap in the bin next to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter between the sinks.
Pick up the pink bar of soap.
Get the soap wet in the right hand sink making sure to turn the faucet off after it's wet.
Walk over and stand in front of the toilet.
Put the soap in the garbage to the right of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter in between the two sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap in between the two sinks and in back of the candle.
Back up from the sink counter slightly.
Place soap in right sink, rinse it, and pick the soap up from the right sink.
Turn around, move towards the door, turn to the right and move towards the window, then turn right and face the toilet.
Place the bar of soap in the rubbish bin in between the toilet and sink counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap in a rubbish bin.
